<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>문의 내역 목록</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/admin/style_check_inquiry.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>


<main class="inquiry-container">


  <table class="inquiry-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>유형</th>
        <th>제목</th>
        <th>상태</th>
        <th>작성일</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <td>기술문의</td>
        <td class="inquiry-title-cell">스마트 약상자 와이파이 연결이 자꾸 끊어집니다.</td>
        <td>
          <span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span>
        </td>
        <td>2026. 07. 02.</td>
      </tr>

      <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <td>배송문의</td>
        <td class="inquiry-title-cell">추가 약통 세트 배송 주소를 변경하고 싶습니다.</td>
        <td>
          <span class="status-badge status-답변대기">답변대기</span>
        </td>
        <td>2026. 07. 01.</td>
      </tr>

      <tr onclick="location.href='/admin/answer_inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <td>서비스문의</td>
        <td class="inquiry-title-cell">부모님 계정과 제 계정을 연동하는 방법이 궁금합니다.</td>
        <td>
          <span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span>
        </td>
        <td>2026. 06. 28.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</main>

</body>
</html>